    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable per the MRL 2 assessment matrix. Hemolysis index predictions satisfy the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across the operating envelope. Residual uncertainty from aleatory sources (patient hematocrit variability, blood analog batch variation) is acknowledged in validation narratives and judged acceptable given the medium model influence and the conservative RH acceptance threshold. The overall evidence package supports acceptance of the CFD model for the stated COU.",
